00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:40,760
Yinzi, come here.

902
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,760
Come eat now.

903
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,800
It's fine, Mother.

904
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,170
I'm not hungry yet.

905
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:47,320
Why is it porridge again?

906
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,880
Working all day like this,

907
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,550
I can't keep going on this.

