938
00:42:30,350 --> 00:42:31,580
How am I pretending?

939
00:42:36,820 --> 00:42:37,910
Let's go eat in our room.

940
00:42:37,910 --> 00:42:38,870
Don't pull me.

941
00:42:40,230 --> 00:42:42,560
Whenever there's trouble,
you try to smooth things over.

942
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:45,400
